    // Header
    header
      .container
        .intro-text
          .intro-lead-in Incredibly Easy To Use!
          .intro-heading Business Automation.
          a#btn-login.page-scroll.btn.btn-xl(href="#", ng-click="login()") Sign In. It's Free.
    // Services Section
    section#services
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.text-center
            h2.section-heading What is GiantCRM?
            h3.section-subheading.text-muted GiantCRM is a customer relationship management (CRM) for online business owners.
        .row.text-center
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-shopping-cart.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Google Contacts, Calendar & Gmail API
            p.text-muted
              | Find Contacts, View & Add Important Upcoming Events & Have a Quick Look at Latest Emails.
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-laptop.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Send Push Notifications Online or Offline.
            p.text-muted
              | Send Latest Promotions to Customers or Reminders To Staff. Android & Chrome on Web Only.
          .col-md-4
            span.fa-stack.fa-4x
              i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x.text-primary
              i.fa.fa-lock.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
            h4.service-heading Get Alternative Views on Customer Reviews
            p.text-muted 
              | Using IBM Watson, You Get To Know Alternative Viewpoints of Your Business's Customer Reviews.
